### 2. 课程计划管理测试 ###

### 2.1 创建课程计划（章节）
POST http://localhost:8080/teachplan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "parentId": 0,
  "level": 1,
  "name": "第一章",
  "orderBy": 1
}

> {% client.global.set("chapterId", response.body.data); %}

### 2.2 创建课程计划（小节）
POST http://localhost:8080/teachplan
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "parentId": "1",
  "level": 2,
  "name": "第一节",
  "orderBy": 1
}

> {% client.global.set("sectionId", response.body.data); %}

### 2.3 查询课程计划树
GET http://localhost:8080/teachplan/tree/{{courseId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 2.4 上移课程计划
POST http://localhost:8080/teachplan/moveup/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 2.5 下移课程计划
POST http://localhost:8080/teachplan/movedown/1
Content-Type: application/json

### 3. 课程教师管理测试 ###

### 3.1 添加课程教师
POST http://localhost:8080/course-teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "organizationId": 1234,
  "name": "测试教师",
  "position": "讲师",
  "description": "测试教师简介",
  "courseIds": ["{{courseId}}"]
}

> {% client.global.set("teacherId", response.body.data); %}

### 3.2 查询课程教师列表
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/list/{{courseId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3.3 查询教师详情
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/1234/86
Content-Type: application/json

### 3.4 查询教师关联的课程
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/courses/{{teacherId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 3.5 查询机构教师列表
GET http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/organization/1234
Content-Type: application/json

### 3.6 修改课程教师
POST http://localhost:8080/course-teacher
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "886",
  "organizationId": 1234,
  "name": "测试教师",
  "position": "高级讲师",
  "description": "修改后的简介",
  "courseIds": ["212"]
}

### 4. 课程审核与发布流程测试 ###

### 4.1 课程预览
GET http://localhost:8080/course/preview/{{courseId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 4.2 提交课程审核
POST http://localhost:8080/course/{{courseId}}/audit/submit
Content-Type: application/json

### 4.3 审核课程（通过）
POST http://localhost:8080/course/audit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "courseId": "{{courseId}}",
  "auditStatus": "202303",
  "auditMind": "课程内容符合要求"
}

### 5. 清理测试数据 ###

### 5.1 解除教师与课程的关联
DELETE http://localhost:8080/course-teacher/{{courseId}}/{{teacherId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5.2 删除课程计划（小节）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/teachplan/{{sectionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 5.3 删除课程计划（章节）
DELETE http://localhost:8080/teachplan/{{chapterId}}
Content-Type: application/json 